{"tid":370662,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"30秒清除電腦系統淤塞的所有垃圾","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T08:30:57.000Z","uid":44333,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cad15c1ab371e606cc28eaa71a760d6f9722697e","tid":370662,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"是否注意到你的電腦系統磁盤的可用空間正在一天天在減少呢？是不是動作一天比一天遲緩呢？<br />\n在Windows在安裝和使用過程中都會產生相當多的垃圾文件，包括臨時文件（如：*.tmp、*._mp）日誌文件（*.log）、臨時幫助文件（*.gid）、磁盤檢查文件（*.chk）、臨時備份文件（如：*.old、*.bak）以及其他臨時文件。特別是如果一段時間不清理IE的臨時文件夾「Temporary Internet Files」，其中的緩存文件有時會佔用上百MB的磁盤空間。這些LJ文件不僅僅浪費了寶貴的磁盤空間，嚴重時還會使系統運行慢如蝸牛。現在就讓我們一起來快速清除系統垃圾吧！！<br />\n下面是步驟很簡單就兩步！<br />\n打開「記事本」，把下面的字複製進去，點「另存為」，把文件名定為「清除系統垃圾.bat」就完成，記住後副檔名一定要是.bat，好ok了！你的垃圾清除器就這樣製作成功了！雙擊它就能很快地清理垃圾文件，大約一分鐘不到。 <br />\n複製下面的字：<br />\n<br />\n@echo off <br />\necho 正在清除系統垃圾文件，請稍等...... <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.tmp <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*._mp <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.log <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.gid <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.chk <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%*.old <br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%recycled*.* <br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%*.bak <br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%prefetch*.* <br />\nrd /s /q %windir%temp &amp; md %windir%temp<br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%cookies*.* <br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%recent*.* <br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%Local SettingsTemporary Internet Files*.*&quot; <br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%Local SettingsTemp*.*&quot; <br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%recent*.*&quot; <br />\necho 清除系統垃圾完成！ <br />\necho. &amp; pause<br />\n<br />\n複製上面的字~~~以後只要雙擊運行該文件，當屏幕提示「清除系統垃圾完成！就還你一個「苗條」的系統了！！到時候再看看你的電腦，是不是急速如飛呢？"},{"pid":"acdee0860daaf588aa93cf12f1d945e607e5a032","tid":370662,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝樓主"},{"pid":"e4ef1176c436e8d4ebd6eb54d5991c8e068d8208","tid":370662,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"跪求清爽版"},{"pid":"d81ad52efd5d3e999733d4b901b28b3a2ef84059","tid":370662,"uid":28515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"999"},{"pid":"cecfcfcb0365f8185f7735aecd064a51a5f22473","tid":370662,"uid":20811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"求加強版"},{"pid":"4ecc72beb1dfc3b6cc2f292b509ca9d287f7ca90","tid":370662,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"54e9dc4b9aa065f29449b85c18c823d9fc0543b8","tid":370662,"uid":11935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b85e566b32829943213e038a4a35179ba562b9","tid":370662,"uid":63396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"*.*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4ad51ab3c8bd6177dee9ff02484f7802c517fa","tid":370662,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"又真係快咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae26d9e276dadf08bf4f0ff8bb423eb402d6ca3d","tid":370662,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"不誠實使用電腦要坐幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedb3eea180de12eef7aadb0bf7297e8dfc1ffd5","tid":370662,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"=.=做乜爆出泥"},{"pid":"fc91ba195eacded60bd6ed6664c78bb71e458536","tid":370662,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:22:46.000Z","msg":"想要清爽版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"